<div class="flex min-h-screen bg-gray-50 p-4">
  <!-- 왼쪽: 폼 -->
  <main class="w-2/3 pr-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-8 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Blind-Boolean SQLi 방어 버전</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Prepared Statement로 파라미터 바인딩</p>
      <form action="/lesson/blind_boolean_secure/query" method="get" class="space-y-4">
        <label class="block text-gray-700">
          Item Name:
          <input
            name="name"
            type="text"
            value="<%= name %>"
            placeholder="예: apple"
            required
            class="w-full mt-1 px-4 py-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring"
          />
        </label>
        <label class="block text-gray-700">
          비교할 문자:
          <input
            name="char"
            type="text"
            value="<%= char %>"
            placeholder="예: s"
            maxlength="1"
            required
            class="w-full mt-1 px-4 py-2 border rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring"
          />
        </label>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full py-2 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-green-700 transition"
        >
          안전 조회
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- 오른쪽: 사용된 SQL 템플릿 -->
  <aside class="w-1/3 pl-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">사용된 SQL</h3>
      <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-sm">
SELECT *
  FROM items
 WHERE name = ?
   AND (SELECT substr(password,1,1)
          FROM users
         WHERE username='admin') = ?;
      </pre>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-xs">
        첫 번째 `?` 에는 Item Name, 두 번째 `?` 에는 비교할 문자(예: s)가<br/>
        안전하게 바인딩됩니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>